and Practice&#8214;, seventh plenary meeting, eighteenth session of the Human Rights Council, 14 
September 2011, available at http://www.ohchr.org/EN/Issues/Solidarity/Pages/Statements.aspx.  </p>

<p><b>A/HRC/23/45/Add.1 
