</p>
<p>17. The consultations and dialogues of the Independent Expert with officials of the 
Government of Brazil have been consolidated into this report, the primary consideration 
being given to the relevance of such information to the policy and practice of international 
solidarity. 
</p>
<p>18. The Independent Expert expresses her deep appreciation to the Government of 
Brazil for providing her the opportunity to observe and learn first-hand what she had only </p>

